{"tid":1554905,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[condom智障] 警隊疑拖加班費杯麵錢","createTime":"2019-09-09T07:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:46:35.000Z","uid":51620,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"fa9b21e1d3ad54799f6adda5aebb8df1e9d4e091","tid":1554905,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:04:15.000Z","msg":"連場示威活動令前線警務人員疲於奔命，消息指有防暴警員投訴加班錢被拖數，認為警隊「補水」速度極慢。所謂三軍未動，糧草先行，各區警署屢被示威者包圍期間，有警員墊支購買即食麵，惟至今仍未能報銷，惹來不滿。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警員超時工作情況愈來愈多，消息指有防暴警員投訴加班錢被拖數，而墊支購買即食麵仍未能報銷。據了解，反修例風波由今年六月開始，六月的加班錢會在六月底申報，並於七月底領取，如此類推，以往多數是刑緝部門的同事申領，近期則多了軍裝人員，相信有警務人員不熟悉申報程序及時間而有感被拖數。至於近期警務人員參與行動，三餐及消夜均由人事部膳食組負責，若有警員墊支購買即食麵，事後可向人事部膳食組申報，惟取回有關款項則需時。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190908/mobile/bkn-20190908033015406-0908_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190908%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190908033015406-0908_00822_001.html&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kRBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=bf8a43ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190908/mobile/bkn-20190908033015406-0908_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f056d34b0a23c3ddbe46328a38d92bf06548a2b5","tid":1554905,"uid":280469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:05:38.000Z","msg":"除左講恭喜之外, 都唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj